#: /chroot/plugins/sg-ai-studio/core/Admin/Admin.php:151
#| msgid ""
#| "Hi! I am your WordPress AI Assistant. How can I help you manage your site "
#| "today? **Here are a few suggestions:** - **Create a new blog post or "
#| "page** with a title, contant and featured image - **Install a plugin** "
#| "like Yoast SEO - **List all active plugins** and their versions on the "
#| "site"
msgid ""
"Hi! I am your WordPress AI Assistant. How can I help you manage your site "
"today?\n"
"\n"
"**Here are a few suggestions:**\n"
"- **Create a new blog post or page** with a title, content and featured "
"image\n"
"- **Install a plugin** like Yoast SEO\n"
"- **List all active plugins** and their versions on the site"
msgstr ""
"Bonjour ! Je suis votre assistant IA WordPress. Comment puis-je vous aider à "
"gérer votre site aujourd'hui ? \n"
"\n"
"**Voici quelques suggestions :** \n"
"- **Créer un nouvel article de blog ou une nouvelle page** avec un titre, un "
"contenu et une image mise en avant \n"
"- **Installer un plugin** comme Yoast SEO \n"
"- **Lister tous les plugins actifs** et leurs versions sur le site"

#: /chroot/plugins/sg-ai-studio/core/Admin/Admin.php:144
#| msgid ""
#| "Hi! I am your WordPress AI Assistant. How can I help you manage your "
#| "store today? **Here are a few suggestions:** - **Create a new product** "
#| "with a price, product image and description - **Summarize today's "
#| "orders** to see your sales - **Generate a sales report** for this month"
msgid ""
"Hi! I am your WordPress AI Assistant. How can I help you manage your store "
"today?\n"
"\n"
"**Here are a few suggestions:**\n"
"- **Create a new product** with a price, product image and description\n"
"- **Summarize today's orders** to see your sales\n"
"- **Generate a sales report** for this month"
msgstr ""
